    "body": "If TileN is not divisible by 32 (e.g, 208), by default EpiTile would be set to 128 x 32, which does not compile as TileN is required to be divisible by EpiTileN. We instead set EpiTileN to be gcd(32, TileN).\r\nCc @thakkarV @hwu36 ",
